{"tid":780373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會展站附近50公共設施　煤氣管水管有沉降","createTime":"2018-08-15T06:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T09:11:26.000Z","uid":23707,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe7eeff335bdec4ed96739b27e21191a23efcad","tid":780373,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180815/bkn-20180815123043131-0815_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180815%2Fbkn-20180815123043131-0815_00822_001.html&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b9bf23e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180815/bkn-20180815123043131-0815_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n灣仔區議會今日(15日)中午舉行特別會議，討論沙中線會展站沉降事宜。會議有20名港鐵及各政府部門代表出席，包括路政署、運輸署、建築署及渠務署等，接受出席會議的6名區議員提問，由於出席議員未達半數，按會議常規不屬正式會議，亦不設會議紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，該站有50個涉及公共設施位置的沉降幅度達至預設指標，當中包括道路、煤氣管、水管及冷卻水管，但附近樓宇的沉降未達指標。港鐵已即時採取措施，例如安裝實時煤氣滲漏監測儀，煤氣公司亦派人巡查。港鐵強調相關指標並非安全上限，亦訂得謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n路政署表示，署方監核顧問就上周六(11日)已實地視察相關沉降超標位置，確定無明顯結構安全問題。"},{"pid":"7504464399fb3dcdb9f2847c3350c0a9876e1552","tid":780373,"uid":22349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"若沉降引發爆炸，就像幾年前高雄的(氣體爆炸)事故一樣，可能成個區都爆炸<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，2014年台灣高雄發生地下氣體喉管洩漏丙烯慘劇，事件釀成大爆炸，造成32人死亡，逾300人受傷，多條主要幹道嚴重損毀。"},{"pid":"a7d9823e4037b5bf77ddbcd3bb3ca3f45a990e49","tid":780373,"uid":693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7504464399fb3dcdb9f2847c3350c0a9876e1552","tid":780373,"uid":22349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"若沉降引發爆炸，就像幾年前高雄的(氣體爆炸)事故一樣，可能成個區都爆炸<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，2014年台灣高雄發生地下氣體喉管洩漏丙烯慘劇，事件釀成大爆炸，造成32人死亡，逾300人受傷，多條主要幹道嚴重損毀。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e852fdfad63ae973dd09d6c00296e57ed0866ff1","tid":780373,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"轟呀"},{"pid":"ecabaa2474748ec458f475f37c200801cfcfd070","tid":780373,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:37:59.000Z","msg":"接受出席會議的6名區議員提問，由於出席議員未達半數，按會議常規不屬正式會議，亦不設會議紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n邊幾隻為左唔留紀錄而唔撚去"},{"pid":"f0c8a1edd1a3bc62b5c027d1169250b4b01f7b39","tid":780373,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7504464399fb3dcdb9f2847c3350c0a9876e1552","tid":780373,"uid":22349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"若沉降引發爆炸，就像幾年前高雄的(氣體爆炸)事故一樣，可能成個區都爆炸<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，2014年台灣高雄發生地下氣體喉管洩漏丙烯慘劇，事件釀成大爆炸，造成32人死亡，逾300人受傷，多條主要幹道嚴重損毀。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:38:09.000Z","msg":"香港人口同D樓比高雄密集好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe7343214f77032e36de945a601192c6c14e230","tid":780373,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"全台暗藏 4千公里油管<br />\n經濟部拒公布 民怒「經我家不讓我知」<br />\n出版時間：2014/08/02<br />\n<br />\n【綜合報導】高雄前鎮大氣爆引發民眾恐慌，各縣市昨全面稽查瓦斯等地下管線安全，目前除了高雄外，新北市、桃園、雲林等地都有石化相關產業，對於各縣市乙烯、丙烯等工業用管線，經濟部能源局竟未統計管理，連全台共4060.5公里的油管，也拒絕公布管線分布狀況，災民痛批：「管線經過我家，不讓我知道，什麼道理！」認為政府應讓管線的路線、維修透明化，更應將分布混亂的地下管線整合管理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20140802/LB18/LB18_003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20140802%2FLB18%2FLB18_003.jpg&h=117be020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宛如戰場 高雄前鎮前晚爆發氣爆，許多縣市都繃緊神經，稽查轄區內油管、石化、天然氣管線。陳為坐攝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/forum/daily/20140802/35996992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fforum%2Fdaily%2F20140802%2F35996992&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b89fe442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fforum%2Fdaily%2F20140802%2F35996992&h=d11d26b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/forum/daily/20140802/35996992</a>"},{"pid":"892c794f965ee8862a277a5a2669093b70fd5ec0","tid":780373,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7d9823e4037b5bf77ddbcd3bb3ca3f45a990e49","tid":780373,"uid":693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7504464399fb3dcdb9f2847c3350c0a9876e1552","tid":780373,"uid":22349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"若沉降引發爆炸，就像幾年前高雄的(氣體爆炸)事故一樣，可能成個區都爆炸<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，2014年台灣高雄發生地下氣體喉管洩漏丙烯慘劇，事件釀成大爆炸，造成32人死亡，逾300人受傷，多條主要幹道嚴重損毀。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"好似以前睇特警新人類會展爆炸嗰一幕咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebba0d2066d93de93eda330a73e1218781a21c3","tid":780373,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"政府繼續講無事,繼續傳下波先"},{"pid":"c476ed350881d5fc89b10eb7dad3019ed1c2038d","tid":780373,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"41edfb61663acd6ba4df7ff8ab2106019c3bbd79","tid":780373,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"等睇建制講佔中示威者過份眾集搞到沉降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4774eb509b4c5efe1c11ef